Wireless sensor/actuator node software for Bluetooth modules
============================================================

This is experimental firmware for CSR BlueCore based Bluetooth modules
allowing a host to control most of the I/O aspectes of a module, thus
allowing for low-cost, flexible, easily accessible solutions for various
remote control and automation tasks.


This source code is released under the terms if GNU General Public License
version 3, http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/gpl.html
